				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Anxiety Rising Over Relations Between Japan and China</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Andrew Ross Sorkin			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-01-28T02:18:44+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">January 27, 2014 9:18 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">January 27, 2014 9:18 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content">
	<div class="w592"><figure class="promo media video blog-video "
